A simple, free application designed for beginner to intermediate students of Russian language to learn vocabulary.

Features
* 2000 words
* Block known words
* View 100 most recent words
* View words on wiktionary.org

See it on the google play store: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=edu.msu.keifcame.russianwordoftheday&hl=en
